Build a Calculator

● Basic Features

○ Addition, Subtraction, Multiplication, Division of integers and floats.
○ Division by zero should display NaN
○ Clear operation should work
○ Decimal values should be formatted for display. (2 decimal places)
○ Integer results should not be displayed as 4.0 instead of 4.

● Advanced Features
○ Maintain history of last 20 operations. (Use Recycler View or List View)
○ Error handling for invalid strings e.g. 1.2.3 , 0..1 , 1. Etc.
○ Clearing the entire text on Long Click and individual characters on Short Click of Clear button
○ Try to replicate the design of your mobile’s calculator app.
